# Project context

Read these before making changes:

- **`CLAUDE.md`** — canonical agent instructions: brief, domain model, stack, conventions, definition of done
- **`DESIGN.md`** — brand/visual spec; lands in code only via `packages/ui/src/styles/globals.css` tokens
- **`README.md`** — human submission doc (how to run, tradeoffs, AI process notes)

Claude Code config and repo-tailored skills live in `.claude/` (`launch.json`, `skills/`). There is no AI workspace package — tool configs point at the docs above; they do not fork them.
